window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Please note: This podcast contains explicit language and mature themes and is intended for adult audiences only. Discretion is advised.</b></p> <p><i>Hit Job</i> follows Brynn Morris (Palmer), an aspiring artist desperate for a job to help her ailing grandmother. As a last resort, she takes a job as an administrative assistant at a company with the motto: “Do Bad Things for Good Reasons.” Joining forces with her awkward tech nerd of a coworker Geo (Davidson), she unexpectedly gets swept up in a company-wide contest that forces her to question her morals. Having a killer job suddenly takes on a whole new meaning.</p> <p>Visit Audible Sounds Funny</p>"; 
